\begin_inset Caption

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Visualization of a simple propagator.
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

\end_layout

\end_inset

For a general polynomial interaction term of the form 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda\phi^{k}\left(\vec{x}\right)$
\end_inset

, this can be visualized by 
\begin_inset Float figure
wide false
sideways false
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\begin_inset ERT
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
